  <div class="faq-section" id="upload">
    <h2 class="heading">Uploading School Data</h2>

    <div class="faq-question">
      <h3>How do I upload data to be processed for my Campus/District?</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-answer">
      <p>Click on the [Upload Data] button on the navigation bar.</p>
      <p>Download the template CSV file from our website.</p>
      <p>Using a CSV editing program, such as Excel or Google Sheets, edit and paste in the corresponding information.</p>
      <p>Save the file locally and make sure it is in the ".csv" format. Then press the "Choose File" button and select the .csv file you just saved.</p>
      <p>Finally, click the "Import" button to process the upload.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

